project_descr: Support the Government of Romania in achieving its development objectives through building a successful tourism sector based on its cultural heritage and environmental assets.

outputs.output_descr: The overall objective of the project is to formulate the elements of a sustainable tourism sector in Baile Herculane, Borsec and Sulina which integrates tourism sector development to local area economic growth and social development.

project_title: integrated urban development for soustainable tourism
